dct_alternative_sm: Populations Which will be served by the Great Southern of Spain Railway irrespective of through traffic
dct_description_sm: Waterlow & Sons Limited London Wall London.
Inset map: "Map of Spain & Portugal" showing railroads.
Shows Almanzora Railroad in red, with mines, forests, quarries, deposits, along its course.
Also regional boundaries, rainage, cities (including unnamed), other railways.
Table showing populations of various cities linked by Great Southern of Spain Railway, with 1877 census statistics.
